title: Celebrity Gossip Part 1 - Jimmy Kimmel Apologized
description: Drew Barrymore found out that Selma Blair had sent her death threats years ago… so Drew said LET’S GET HER ON MY TALK SHOW! Sounds awkward, right? And Jimmy Kimmel apologized to Quinta Brunson for pretending to be passed out drunk while she was giving her Emmy acceptance speech.
